webXBMC
---------------

webXBMC is a webinterface for XBMC with PVR Support.

Communication to XBMC is done with xbmc-php-rpc from Karl Rixon <karl@karlrixon.co.uk>.

Jura was designed by Daniel Johnson.  Please send any bug reports or glyph
requests to il.basso.buffo@gmail.com.

