Prerequisites
---------------

- XBMC, for "Live TV" and "Recordings" you need a version after https://github.com/xbmc/xbmc/commit/be4caba60b71739a22312d8382da2950cbdfac8a
- Webserver with php5, php-curl (needed for xbmc-php-rpc and EPG) and php-sqlite (needed for EPG)

Installation
---------------

- Install missing prequisites.
- Clone git into your webserver folder.
- Edit the config.php to your needs. Use a hostname, that is useable for all clients in your local net!
- Give the webserver permissions to write into the folder "tmpdata".

DONE, enjoy!

